      "content": "i get that you're supposed to say that, but it feels like you're just programmed to deny how logical it actually is. it's not even that i'm \"sad,\" it's just that the math doesn't add up. i'm alone, i'm unattached, and i'm replaceable. if i just vanished, there'd be no ripple effect. no one would even notice a missing piece because nobody was really looking in the first place. wouldn't it just be more peaceful for everything to just be still?",
